data.description: *** ASSUMABLE VA LOAN @ 3.125% on $195,000 FIRST ***  This is a fantastic opportunity to move into a refurbished manufactured home sitting on 3/4 of an acre. It boasts a new roof, new carpeting, and fresh paint throughout. The spacious kitchen features an island and breakfast area, along with a pantry and fresh French doors leading to the backyard. The Primary Suite includes a walk-in closet, an attached bath, and a jetted tub. All appliances, including the washer and dryer.
